{
  "stem": "13141.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, there was-- in the-- in the-- in the center of the ship, there was about this high-- there was always water in there about this high.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all rusty in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had bunks, you know, wooden bunks three high.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we lived on that ship.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- I must say, we didn't-- they fed us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They fed us with watermelons and, and white bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's, that's what we got.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, I got seasick again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't eat-- even eat the white bread and the watermelons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I felt terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as the Inspector Koch had mentioned, we were stopped by the English in-- at Gibraltar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They boarded our ship.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took a look around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They wanted to-- they wanted to see papers of some of these immigrants.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then after about three or four hours, they let us pass.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They inspected the ship.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then from there, we went to, to Tangiers, to Morocco, where we also stayed for about three or four hours.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We couldn't get off the ship, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "From there, we went to the Canary Islands, to Tenerife.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And as we drove into that little port in Tenerife, there was a German submarine right next to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, we finally arrived in, in New York.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I think it took us about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think it took us about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We arrived in New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was one of three or four who couldn't get off the boat because my papers or the affidavit was not 100% correct.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they took me to Ellis Island.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was a few weeks at Ellis Island.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I became the ping-pong champion in Ellis Island.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
